## Change 2 — `frontend/src/main.rs`: Fix `App`'s `use_effect`

Set `is_loading = true` before spawning, and properly reset `AUTH` on `Err`:

```rust
use_effect(move || {
    if api::is_logged_in() && !auth::AUTH.read().is_authenticated {
        auth::AUTH.write().is_loading = true;
        spawn(async move {
            match api::get_me().await {
                Ok(resp) => {
                    *auth::AUTH.write() = auth::AuthState::logged_in(resp.data);
                }
                Err(_) => {
                    api::clear_token();
                    *auth::AUTH.write() = auth::AuthState::logged_out();
                }
            }
        });
    }
});
```

