## Change 3 — `frontend/src/layouts/mod.rs`: Add auth guard to `MainLayout`

Add `use_navigator()` and a `use_effect` that redirects to login when unauthenticated. Add early returns for loading and unauthenticated states. Import `LoadingSpinner` from `crate::components`.

```rust
use dioxus::prelude::*;
use crate::auth::AUTH;
use crate::api;
use crate::components::LoadingSpinner;

#[component]
pub fn MainLayout() -> Element {
    let auth = AUTH.read();
    let has_token = api::is_logged_in();
    let nav = use_navigator();

    let needs_redirect = !auth.is_loading && !auth.is_authenticated && !has_token;
    use_effect(move || {
        if needs_redirect {
            nav.replace(crate::Route::Login {});
        }
    });

    if auth.is_loading {
        return rsx! {
            div { class: "app-container",
                main { class: "main-content",
                    LoadingSpinner { message: "Loading session..." }
                }
            }
        };
    }

    if !auth.is_authenticated {
        // Effect will fire nav.replace(Login) after this render
        return rsx! {
            div { class: "app-container",
                main { class: "main-content",
                    LoadingSpinner {}
                }
            }
        };
    }

    // Authenticated — render full layout (sidebar unchanged)
    rsx! {
        div { class: "app-container",
            nav { class: "sidebar",
                // ... existing sidebar content unchanged ...
            }
            main { class: "main-content with-sidebar",
                Outlet::<crate::Route> {}
            }
        }
    }
}
```

The existing sidebar content (header, nav links, footer with user info + logout) is kept exactly as-is — only the outer conditional structure changes.

---

## Behavior After Fix

| Scenario | Result |
|----------|--------|
| Fresh visit to `/dashboard` with no token | Spinner briefly → redirect to `/login` |
| Hard reload on `/dashboard` with valid token | Spinner during hydration → full page loads |
| Hard reload with expired token | Spinner → `get_me()` fails → token cleared → `AUTH` reset → redirect to `/login` |
| Same-session login → hard redirect | Token + `is_loading=true` → spinner → `get_me()` → full page |
| Direct visit to `/login` | Login page renders (outside `MainLayout`, no guard fires) |

---

## Critical Files
- `frontend/src/main.rs` — Route enum + App use_effect
- `frontend/src/layouts/mod.rs` — MainLayout auth guard

## Verification
1. `docker compose up` to start all services
2. Visit `/dashboard` without logging in → should redirect to `/login`
3. Log in → should reach `/dashboard` correctly
4. Hard-reload `/dashboard` while logged in → should stay on `/dashboard` (spinner briefly)
5. Manually expire/delete the token in localStorage → reload → should redirect to `/login`
"}

