- `test_reschedule_conflict_detection_excludes_self` — the self-exclusion filter works correctly
- `test_reschedule_conflict_with_other_booking_detected` — conflict with a different booking is caught
- `test_max_reschedules_boundary` — at `MAX_RESCHEDULES` the attempt is rejected before hitting the DB
- `test_reschedule_requires_confirmed_status` — only `confirmed` bookings are reschedulable

