- `test_course_unpublish_entity_type_included` — `'course_unpublish'` matches
- `test_other_entity_type_excluded` — `'resource'` does not match
- `test_pending_step1_status_included` — correct statuses pass
- `test_pending_step2_status_included`
- `test_approved_status_excluded` — `'approved'` is not in the pending set

